  "title": "Corporate Secretary QI (RQI)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking to engage a Company Secretary on a long-term monthly retainer basis.</p><p><strong>Preferred:</strong> a Singapore Registered Qualified Individual (RQI).<br /><strong>If not an RQI:</strong> you should meet the eligibility requirements to apply for RQI , and preferably have corporate secretarial services experience.</p><p><strong>Scope of work (low volume; mainly oversight and review)</strong></p><p>We have internal standard processes and checklists in place.  You will be engaged as our RQI to provide compliance oversight and document review for client companies’ routine corporate governance matters and filings with ACRA (and other relevant authorities), as applicable.</p><p>We do not expect any work before March (the guaranteed retainer will still be paid). For the following six months, the expected workload is no more than 5 cases per month. The guaranteed monthly retainer may be increased after the first six months, subject to business volume.</p><p><strong>Engagement & remuneration</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Guaranteed monthly retainer:</strong> SGD<strong> 500 </strong>per month (payable regardless of whether there are any active cases)</li><li><strong>Additional fee:  8% </strong>of the fees paid by client companies on your monthly oversight/review list</li></ul><p><strong>Working arrangement</strong></p><p>Remote work with flexible hours. Communications will mainly be via email / WhatsApp / online meetings.</p><p><strong>If either party wishes to end the cooperation, please provide at least one (1) month’s prior written notice.</strong></p>",
